This module is the Trust engine of the SLA trust manager of Vital project.

it fetch data about fulfilment of each SLA provided by the SLA manager REST interface.

The fulfilment data and the trust scores are stored in a MongoDB. At this stage this DB should be installed in the same server than this servr is running
with the configuration of Default mongo port and no user/pwd.

To install this functionality it is only required to deploy it as a WAR file into the Wildfly server.

